\n屈就啲做返個市委<br />\n之後殺上去湖南<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當你周街聲講你係市委<br />\n咩女都即卡濕曬<br />\n黑社會都即卡拉返條女俾你<br />\n<br />\n幾體現到大陸啲人幾尊重官<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9f3c7652fab1d5e035055711acf5e63cbf1832c","tid":439193,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T00:33:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佢細我一年, 湖南人, 唔靚但細細粒好cutie<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁有次做完part b後, 佢突然間問我: 有跟女孩子做過那事嗎?<br />\n我話無<br />\n第二日佢way鮮叫我book間房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住我地就做左愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做完之後我有啲錯愕, 問佢要幾錢?<br />\n佢居然即刻聲淚俱下咁話自己不是妓女, 我們現在是情人所以才做這事的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我開心到幾日無打過飛機, 之後同佢再出去食左幾餐飯<br />\n到禮拜六, 佢突然間話老豆喺湖南得罪黑社會, 要匯幾十萬過去<br />\n我即刻將呢幾年做pt, 利是錢, 車船津貼, 加埋港幣九萬過哂畀佢<br />\n之後way鮮, 電話就一路聯絡唔到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無人估到點解會咁? 佢會唔會是畀啲大陸佬捉走左? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n請參考6千成主席潮文<br />\n當然中間有個元老已經升仙<br />\n屈就啲做返個市委<br />\n之後殺上去湖南<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當你周街聲講你係市委<br />\n咩女都即卡濕曬<br />\n黑社會都即卡拉返條女俾你<br />\n<br />\n幾體現到大陸啲人幾尊重官<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最大既黑社會？"},{"pid":"cb755b9367b2d9125e2d719431d13e40914605ae","tid":439193,"uid":38583,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T00:42:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">左<span style=\"color: red;\">✗ <strong>咗</strong></span><br />\n畀佢破<span style=\"color: red;\">✗ <strong>俾佢破</strong></span><br />\n咁<span style=\"color: red;\">✗ <strong>噉</strong></span><br />\nway鮮<span style=\"color: red;\">✗ <strong>微信</strong></span><br />\n哂<span style=\"color: red;\">✗ <strong>晒